Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:33.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.22,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.83,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,180.389)}The Killer Queen Ant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.83,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(557.167,670.389)}Arichimedes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:33.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's scientists have succeeded\Nin creating a cyborg from an ant egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the birth of the cyborg\Nqueen ant, Arichimedes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol, use her to bring\NJapan under Shocker's control!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall promptly put\NArichimedes's power to the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H37B1E4&\fs60}Tonan Bank, Jonan Branch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency in the underground vault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The vault has been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the power of the queen ant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This deadly laser network will kill\Nanyone who approaches this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have this network in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kamen Rider won't be able to get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't forget the\NKamen Rider's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The research we're doing here will\Nall go to waste if we're exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Once this research pays off,\Nall of Japan will belong to Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me... remain on high alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... they almost saw me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Going somewhere without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve,\Nheading off without telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tailed you in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, this thing picked up\Na mystery signal coming from the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we get past the\Nkiller laser network?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That branch... over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the password?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The signal is coming from this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shocker must be hiding\Nsomething important,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if they have defenses like these in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:06:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange... Let's look in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The signal's coming from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge egg...\NI've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the source of the signal\Nyou were picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's Shocker's game here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they digging up monster\Neggs and trying to hatch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it's made out of iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's clear Shocker's\Nusing them for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's carry them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What good would that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We can run a more thorough analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,An alarm system!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My leg... my leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Return my egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You show yourself, Ichimonji Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborg... fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... take the egg and flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ant colony!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute I give the order,\Nthose ants will devour you whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the queen ant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer ants that I lead\Nwill tear Japan to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, devour Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:10:02.99,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape me, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like my body's on fire... the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of my power?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,While you were wasting time fighting\NRider, they took the egg away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hokkaido, Tohoku, Chugoku, Shikoku, Kyushu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd prepared to send more\Nant queens to every region of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But your foolish mistake\Nhas thrown a wrench in our plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I will retrieve the stolen egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it costs me my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... I will trust you\Nand give you another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But only one chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I find Taki Kazuya, I'll find the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All together, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,An egg, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it is on the large side...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How many could you feed\Nwith an omelet like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't make a dent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I took that egg from a Shocker lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And you're bringing it here?\NThat's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to store it in\Nthe warehouse for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang onto it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. Goro, help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to hatch into\Na monster in the meantime, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, you're such a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch too much TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was a real egg,\Nwe'd have such a big omelet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did Hayato go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's putting the responsibility on\Nus, as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining and watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting us on egg duty...\Nlike we're just a bunch of hens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That Ichimonji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! You have a phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. I finished the analysis\Non the fluid that hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's formic acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Formic acid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That dissolving acid produced by ants?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But producing enough formic\Nacid to coat a human body
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,would require hundreds\Nof thousands of ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shocker is breeding ants at that scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And that egg is a queen ant egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it shows any signs of\Nchanging, evacuate at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dealt it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do anything so disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman, the egg is\Nputting out that smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The egg is changing colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Pandora's Box about to open...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time for poetry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is seriously bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ichimonji... if Shocker is\Nmaking a queen ant-human cyborg,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,what's their endgame?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ant swarms follow the orders of their\Nqueen, devouring grass and trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrifying... What a terrifying plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly! The egg is changing color!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taki, run!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was dreading this might happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to see what comes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if you value your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ants...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming in through the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight them to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ant monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet fire will hurt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The ants are retreating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato here. Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ichimonji... thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! That isn't Hayato's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Run!\N- Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared... We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster must be after that egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pour gasoline on it and burn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, hold the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... it can even survive the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll feed all five of you to my ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, my ants! Devour them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Arichimedes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plans are through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... you survived, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I will send you to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow Shocker to conquer Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll melt you into sludge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Return my egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A chain reaction is causing\Nthe eggs to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has foiled us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman! The ants are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Had a nice workout, did you, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better split!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:32.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider had stopped Shocker's\Nplot to conquer Japan once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:37.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Colonel Zol would continue\Nto forward his evil plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:41.08,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.44,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,470.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:45.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:47.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the mummy monster Egyptas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.31,0:23:49.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The monster Egyptas, awakened\Nfrom a 4000-year slumber,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:54.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,will battle with Rider over\Nthe fate of billion-yen gemstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:56.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.19,0:24:01.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Revived Mummy Monster, Egyptas!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:01.06,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,200.389)}The Revived Mummy Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:01.06,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,660.389)}Egyptas!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:10.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:15.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:18.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:20.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.93,0:24:22.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:26.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:28.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:34.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:37.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:41.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.83,0:24:45.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Killer Queen Ant, Arichimedes